title: Letter from Tisha Taylor to a publication editor
description: A letter penned by Tish Taylor to a publication editor about the Black, queer experience. Tisha mentions how The Darts Over Missouri League barred Soakies from playing in their event, connecting it to the racist views people held about the bar. She ends her letter with a call to action to cease ties with bigoted companies, proclaiming, "We are proud, Black, and strong".
